<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Molecular_rendering.jpg" class="image" title="Molecular rendering.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Molecular_rendering.jpg/120px-Molecular_rendering.jpg" width="120" height="120" border="0" /></a></div>
