<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:YF-17_aircraft_Plot.jpg" class="image" title="YF-17 aircraft Plot.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/YF-17_aircraft_Plot.jpg/120px-YF-17_aircraft_Plot.jpg" width="120" height="120" border="0" /></a></div>
