<p><a name="Scientific_visualization_organizations" id="Scientific_visualization_organizations"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Scientific_visualization&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Scientific visualization organizations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Scientific visualization organizations</span></h2>
<p>Important laboratory in the field are:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Electronic_Visualization_Laboratory" title="Electronic Visualization Laboratory">Electronic Visualization Laboratory</a></li>
<li>NASA Goddard Scientific Visualization Studio.<sup id="cite_ref-33" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-33" title=""><span>[</span>34<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
<p>Conferences in this field are:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Eurographics" title="Eurographics">Eurographics</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Graphicon" title="Graphicon" class="mw-redirect">Graphicon</a>: the largest computer graphics conference in the former Soviet Union</li>
<li>IEEE Visualization conferences</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/SIGGRAPH" title="SIGGRAPH">SIGGRAPH</a>: world biggest computer graphics conference</li>
</ul>
<p>See further: <a href="/wiki/Category:Computer_graphics_organizations" title="Category:Computer graphics organizations">Category:Computer graphics organizations</a></p>
